    "causal_summary": "The `external/` folder of this packet contains the public Xanther Context Engine (XCE) integration repository — README, MIT license, MCP configs for 5 IDEs, and 3 steering files (`CLAUDE.md`, `kiro.md`, `opencode-prompt.txt`). XCE is a hosted SaaS MCP server that delivers architectural context (HLD, LLD, component descriptions, call graphs, impact analysis) via 5 tool primitives, claiming +7.4pp on SWE-bench Verified for Sonnet 4.0 and ~20% token reduction when steering rules are active. The underlying PRAT (Persistent Recursive Abstract Tree) algorithm is closed-source.",
